description: Strathmore Plus Uranium Corp., an exploration stage company, engages in the acquisition, exploration, and development of resource properties. The company holds interests in the Night Owl property and Agate project located in the Shirley Basin Uranium District, Wyoming. It also holds interest in the Beaver Rim project that includes 131 unpatented lode mining claims covering an area of 1,095 hectares located in the Gas Hills Uranium District, Central Wyoming. The company was formerly known as Strathmore Plus Energy Corp. Strathmore Plus Uranium Corp. was incorporated in 2007 and is based in Kelowna, Canada.
